card.name: Statistics since moment of creating transaction

native.query:
WITH tr as (select CREATED_AT
                 , ID
                 , USER_ID
                 , WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME
                 , CONFIRMED
            from MART.TRANSACTIONS
            where TYPE_MAIN in ('buy', 'sell')
              and WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME is not null
              and {{WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME}} 
              and {{Pay_system}}
              and {{vendor_name}}
              and ({{antifraud_status}} or type in ('sell', 'buy_acquirer'))
              ),
     first_tr as (select USER_ID, min(CREATED_AT) as first_transaction
                  from tr
                  group by 1),
     filter_data as (select ID
     from MART.TRANSACTIONS
      where TYPE_MAIN in ('buy', 'sell')
              and WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME is not null 
              and {{CREATED_AT}}),
     type_user as (select tr.CREATED_AT
                        , tr.ID
                        , tr.USER_ID
                        , tr.WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME
                        , tr.CONFIRMED
                        , CASE
                              WHEN first_tr.first_transaction = tr.CREATED_AT
                                  THEN 'new user'
                              ELSE 'old user' END type_user
                   from tr
                            inner join first_tr as first_tr on tr.USER_ID = first_tr.USER_ID
                            inner join filter_data on filter_data.id = tr.id)

select date_trunc('month', CREATED_AT) as dt_month
     , type_user
     , count(distinct USER_ID) as count_users_created_transaction
     , count(distinct case when CONFIRMED then USER_ID end) as count_users_completed_transaction
     , count(distinct case when CONFIRMED then USER_ID end)/count(distinct USER_ID) as acceptance_rate_users
     , count(ID) as count_transaction
     , count(case when CONFIRMED then id end) as complete_transaction
     , count(case when CONFIRMED then id end)/count(id) as acceptance_rate_transactions
     , count(ID)/count(distinct USER_ID) as created_transaction_per_user
     , case when count(distinct case when CONFIRMED then USER_ID end) > 0
     then count(case when CONFIRMED then id end)/count(distinct case when CONFIRMED then USER_ID end) end as completed_transaction_per_user
from type_user
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

visualization_settings.text:
How we count new and old user:
we count user first transaction how new user's transaction and his second (or any next) transaction how old user
But then we will count new and old users - this sum doesn't equal the real count of users.
For example, we have 10 users: 3 of them made 1 transaction and other 7 users returned to Mercuryo and made more transactions
we will count this way:
new users - 10 users with their first transaction 
old users - 3 users with their second, third and other transaction

Now dashboard has filter for only TrustWallet - but you can filter for any partner.
Calculation are only for last 3 months
Because of bug we have problems with calculation since April 2023 to June 2023 and convertion rate will be lower than reality
First way of dividing new / old (returned user)
Second way of dividing new / old (returned user)

How we count new and old user: 
new users - users who have only one transaction
old users - users who have ,more than 1 transactions

User can move from new to old user if he created second reansaction

Now dashboard has filter for only TrustWallet - but you can filter for any partner. Calculation are only for last 3 months Because of bug we have problems with calculation since April 2023 to June 2023 and convertion rate will be lower than reality

Sum of new and old users equal of unique users per month

card.name: Statistics since moment of creating transaction by country

native.query:
WITH tr as (select TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT
                 , TRANSACTIONS.ID
                 , TRANSACTIONS.USER_ID
                 , TRANSACTIONS.WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME
                 , TRANSACTIONS.CONFIRMED
                 , first_value(coalesce(TRANSACTIONS.CARD_ISOCOUNTRY, 'no country')) over (partition by USER_ID order by TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT) as country_user
            from MART.TRANSACTIONS
            where TYPE_MAIN in ('buy', 'sell')
              and TRANSACTIONS.WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME is not null
              and {{WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME}} and
                  {{Pay_system}} and
                  {{vendor_name}} and
                  ({{antifraud_status}}  or type in ('sell', 'buy_acquirer'))
              ),
     top_50_country as (
     WITH filter_50 as (
     select country_user
     , count(distinct tr.id) as count_tr
     from TR
     group by 1
     order by 2 desc
     )
     select country_user
     , row_number() over (order by count_tr desc) as rn
     from filter_50
     ),
     first_tr as (select USER_ID, min(CREATED_AT) as first_transaction
                  from tr
                  group by 1),
     filter_data as (select ID
     from MART.TRANSACTIONS
      where TYPE_MAIN in ('buy', 'sell')
              and WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME is not null 
              and {{CREATED_AT}}),
     type_user as (select tr.CREATED_AT
                        , tr.ID
                        , tr.USER_ID
                        , tr.WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME
                        , tr.CONFIRMED
                        , CASE
                              WHEN first_tr.first_transaction = tr.CREATED_AT
                                  THEN 'new user'
                              ELSE 'old user' END type_user
                        , CASE 
                              WHEN rn <= 50
                                  THEN top_50_country.country_user
                              ELSE 'other countries' END top_50_country
                   from tr
                            inner join first_tr as first_tr on tr.USER_ID = first_tr.USER_ID
                            inner join filter_data on filter_data.id = tr.id
                            inner join top_50_country on top_50_country.country_user = tr.country_user),
main_stat as (
select top_50_country
     , type_user
     , count(distinct USER_ID) as count_users_created_transaction
     , count(distinct case when CONFIRMED then USER_ID end) as count_users_completed_transaction
     , count(distinct case when CONFIRMED then USER_ID end)/count(distinct USER_ID) as acceptance_rate_users
     , count(ID) as count_transaction
     , count(case when CONFIRMED then id end) as complete_transaction
     , count(case when CONFIRMED then id end)/count(id) as acceptance_rate_transactions
     , count(ID)/count(distinct USER_ID) as created_transaction_per_user
     , case when count(distinct case when CONFIRMED then USER_ID end) > 0
     then count(case when CONFIRMED then id end)/count(distinct case when CONFIRMED then USER_ID end) end as completed_transaction_per_user
from type_user
group by 1,2),
sort_stat as (
select top_50_country, sum(count_users_created_transaction) as sum_count_users_created_transaction
from main_stat
group by 1)

select main_stat.top_50_country
     , type_user
     , count_users_created_transaction
     , count_users_completed_transaction
     , acceptance_rate_users
     , count_transaction
     , complete_transaction
     , acceptance_rate_transactions
     , created_transaction_per_user
     , completed_transaction_per_user
from main_stat
left join sort_stat on main_stat.top_50_country = sort_stat.top_50_country
order by sort_stat.sum_count_users_created_transaction desc, type_user

            left join mart.users on users.user_id = WEBAPP_WIDGET_CALCULATIONS_LOG.user_id
            where WEBAPP_WIDGET_CALCULATIONS_LOG.USER_ID is not null

         then count(case when CONFIRMED then id end)/count(distinct case when CONFIRMED then USER_ID end)

from type_user
group by 1,2),
sort_stat as (
